{{PIE root|en|preyH}}
Borrowed from {{bor|en|es|filibustero||[[pirate]]}}, from {{der|en|fr|flibustier}}, from {{der|en|nl|vrijbuiter||[[freebooter]]}}, from {{m|nl|vrij||[[free]]}} + {{m|nl|buit||[[booty]]}} + {{m|nl|-er||agent}}. The word has the same construction as, and is cognate to, {{cog|en|freebooter}}.

